sentences: Adam Kury (born July 7, 1969) is an American bassist and vocalist.
Based in Los Angeles, California, he has been the bassist for Candlebox since the band reunited in 2008.
He currently works in numerous projects/bands including The Kings Royal, Dave Giles, 7th Sun, and Whipped Cream.
